# core-be src architecture

Owner: **CLAUDE.md** (Architecture Rules · Domain Structure · Dependency Rules · Drizzle) + the **[domain-generator](../skills/domain-generator/SKILL.md)** skill.

- Layers: routes → controller → service → repository. Controllers **coordinate**; services express intent (may `withTransaction`) but own no SQL; repositories own SQL. Postgres is the only source of truth.
- **Cross-domain** access goes through the other domain's **service** only (never its repository/schema). Imports use `@/` / `@tooling/`, never `../` (see import-paths).
- Drizzle columns **snake_case**, tables plural; schema files co-located `*.schema.ts`.
- Events (in-process bus) vs BullMQ workers (pull-based) — see the workers-events skill.

